     - Resilience vs security. Strict stateful validation fails when the store is down.
   * - 13
     - GAuth Federation governance — Who maintains the GAuth Issuer Registry at ``gimelfoundation.com/registry``? What are the criteria for inclusion? Should there be a community governance process?
     - Trust framework. The registry is a trust anchor — its governance model matters.

